Title: The Empty Planet (1)
Plot: Clyde and Rani awake to find they are the only humans on Earth, even Sarah Jane Smith has vanished. But the Earth is not deserted, stalking the streets of London, strange forces gather.
GuestStars: Jocelyn Jee Esien, Ace Bhatti, Joe Maso, Paul Kasey, Ruari Mears, Jon Glover
